&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tic Tac Toe</title><link>https://vijay.eu/projects/tic-tac-toe/</link><pubDate>Wed, 02 Jul 2025 15:20:07 +0300</pubDate><guid>https://vijay.eu/projects/tic-tac-toe/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Created it using Google Gemini CLI on 2nd Jul 2025
